{"tid":657892,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"又係飛蟻活躍時間啦","createTime":"2018-05-08T13:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T11:44:05.000Z","uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ba65928b8956680f49ad82e9ea37828160b26953","tid":657892,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"飛蟻又名大水蟻，兩者均是繁殖型白蟻的俗稱，通常指翅膀未脫落前的白蟻，外型雖然和螞蟻相近，但其實在分類學上卻相距甚遠；前者屬於等翅目，後者則屬於膜翅目。飛蟻會在夏天的晚上飛出巢外交配，因喜愛燈光，常被燈光吸引而飛入宅內，通常出現於下雨天。[1][2]飛蟻的生殖能力十分強，約在下雨天會長出有四隻小翼。準備交配繁殖，雌性將會變成蟻后。一對雌雄繁殖蟻飛入民居後會脫掉翅膀鑽進陰暗木罅、門縫之類的地方交配及產卵,繁殖下一代的白蟻。由於白蟻以蛀食木材維生，會對木製的建築物產生損害，可造成巨大破壞。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前唔知飛蟻就係白蟻，直到屋企廚廁門框同幅牆都被蟲蛀，後來見到有白蟻躝過先知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻搵滅蟲公司搞，佢地用個鑽鑽出一個個窿，再打d毒藥入牆到，過咗幾日都無再見有白蟻即係成功滅哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過多一兩年廚房牆拆埋改開放式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdc63d5353f11c38b4c09dbdb7eb682924dcdbb","tid":657892,"uid":41922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"尋日落完雨，今日返到公司勁撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲仆街仲要開窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad94030b61389c51e87d0624129c7e52e16b9a90","tid":657892,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:47:34.000Z","msg":"屋企有幾隻飛蟻飛來飛去，好在拍死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c48e3a68f1b539ba8438e122e03fb522f9b4c26","tid":657892,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母多撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點應對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7058e97dc26f66fc88555ab2f872ef31119d7af9","tid":657892,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"活捉拆翼，睇住佢哋喺地下典吓典吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fea295e37b659d8421d74363e59e66e69b1a0c2","tid":657892,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c48e3a68f1b539ba8438e122e03fb522f9b4c26","tid":657892,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母多撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點應對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:27:22.000Z","msg":"電蚊拍乙個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d494af6e22a1b5850b4bcb54ae51032073e7ab","tid":657892,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T11:44:05.000Z","msg":"今日啲飛蟻超大隻，成條街都係兜口兜面撞埋黎"}]}